# Input string

  Length:
    0.                        [property zerovalue] [single] [error]
    1.                        [error]
    size - 1.
    size + 1.
    size*2.
    size*2 - 1.
    size*2 + 1.
    maxint.                   [single]

  Content:
    alphanumeric characters.  [if !zerovalue]
    special characters.       [if !zerovalue] [error]
    spaces.                   [if !zerovalue] [error]

